{
  "stem": "2226.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know if you heard, but they are a very rich family-- Polanski.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were born in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Like here, we would say, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I took them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And soon, we came at the bridge.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to go to another side of Warsaw past the-- past the [INAUDIBLE], you know, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they had a-- what you call it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like here, Ontario, a-- a lake.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to-- so they-- but they bombed the bridge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They bombed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They bombed the bridge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, I couldn't go through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got to another little city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the little city, we went far-- far to-- to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's another city.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bialystok was already-- the-- the Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They tried to make an army come back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, the Germans came and bombed it again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we ran away as far right straight to the border, Russian-Polish border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That border at that time was Rovno.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- between-- I don't know if you've heard of  the city Kobryn where [INAUDIBLE] was born and-- and another city, Terespol, Kovel, Lodz, the little cities that we pressed through never these airplanes.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we came to Rovno, and they said, OK, here we gonna stop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here, we're going to get everybody-- every Polish from the army together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're gonna go back, fight the German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the meantime, Germans come and threw bombs and explode the whole city because they-- they-- they brought everything to-- to Rovno-- the tanks, with the guns, with everything.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was exactly 15 days the war was done-- 16, or 17 days, exactly on Yom Kippur-- Kippur day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember there were children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't have nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we bought a goose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So who is going to kill it?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
